data.description: Welcome to 119 Forest Ridge Way, a haven of modern elegance nestled within Greenville's esteemed Forest Ridge Community. This immaculate residence, encompassing 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, spans just under 1,500 square feet of thoughtful design and upscale living. Approaching the property, the architectural shingle roof, exterior stone accents, 2-car attached garage, and inviting front porch with swing immediately showcase the attention to detail. Step inside to discover a world of comfort with 9-foot ceilings and luxurious LVP flooring that graces the entire living space. The heart of the home is a chef's dream kitchen, adorned with granite countertops, 42" Cambridge cabinetry featuring large crown molding, and an upgraded Frigidaire Gallery stainless steel appliance package. The family room, boasting a cathedral ceiling with a ceiling fan, and a raised hearth fireplace with a stone-to-wood mantle, creates a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The primary bedroom is a retreat of tranquility, featuring a tray ceiling and a ceiling fan for added comfort. The primary bathroom is a spa-like escape with a double-sink vanity, a garden tub, and a separate shower enclosed by a framed sliding door. This home also prioritizes security with a comprehensive security system, including outdoor cameras. The outdoor living space is equally impressive, featuring a 16' X 12' screened-in patio, providing a perfect setting for outdoor gatherings. Situated on a corner lot at the end of a cul-de-sac, this home offers a unique sense of privacy as it backs up to serene woods. The front lawn, sodded and meticulously maintained, benefits from an irrigation system, ensuring a lush and inviting curb appeal. Experience the perfect blend of sophistication, convenience, and tranquility in one of Greenville's most sought-after communities. Schedule your private tour today!
